data.description: Picturesque piece of lower Keys serenity waiting to welcome you home! This tastefully renovated home is located down a low traffic road in horse country and sprawls over acre with no neighbors in sight. This charming 4 bedrooms 3 bathroom home is well kept and features soaring wood beam ceilings with an open floorplan boasting tranquil views of tropical vegetation from every window. Cook up your fresh catch of the day in the well-appointed kitchen, with ample prep space on the spacious center island or relax in the oversized great room equipped with sliding glass doors leading out to the screened in porch. Your guests will be accommodated in 3 spacious bedrooms, while you retire to large light filled primary suite complete with ensuite bathroom featuring custom tile accents. Wind down on your expansive deck, perfect for entertaining, gardening or simply relaxing in the balmy breezes. Enjoy jaw-dropping views of a starry night sky, unencumbered by light pollution, and devoid of neighborhood or road noise. The house also features a concrete cistern of 13,700 gallons, allowing a multitude of options for cost savings on utilities, environmentally friendly irrigation, or emergency water supply. Large and versatile storage under the home to secure and protect all your tools and toys. Beautiful mature landscaping, with vast areas available for cultivating or yard activities, with plenty of off-road parking available. Located next-door to the Southernmost Riding Club, this home is also located in a ''horse friendly zoning'' area which permits owners to keep horses on site. This is your chance to own a little slice of paradise in the Lower Florida Keys.
